{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：12:22 2026-05-01 HKT<br/>發佈時間：12:22 2026-05-01 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：12:22 2026-05-01 HKT</p><img alt=\"楊偉亨攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0d8aab7e9062dcb0ea80dda1e7fb03e1/2026-05/1_3_0.jpg\"/><p>今日是宏福苑宏泰閣、宏建閣最後一日上樓執拾。住宏泰閣的徐先生及妻子，今早上樓回家，看見自己家園燒毀程度較想像中好，「情況OＫ嘅」。，徐太指客廳及廚房燒得較嚴重，其他部分都OＫ，又表示已拾回有紀念價值的相片。</p><img alt=\"居民上樓執拾。楊偉亨攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c03d7da0baaea1a6cfda4eac9c2d4cc1/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260501_101259483_01.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f5f71bb2426cd359adb948cdbd9daa0f/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260501_101259483_04.jpg\"/><img alt=\"徐先生及太太表示已執回有紀念價值的相片。楊偉亨攝\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8a925932c5366a1fe6781cb799e9a9ff/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260501_114300352.jpg\"/><img alt=\"有宏泰閣居民慶幸拾回陳皮及花膠的物品。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/151af5b916c989137477b1c4e54fece6/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260501_115902040.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/334f93076717ac340f2c082393688125/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260501_115925229.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e0df8201b705d7d948c9da558fa82f75/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260501_115935719.jpg\"/><img alt=\"居民帶走花膠等海味。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e70da8478c9ac888593ca79d546f11b/2026-05/KakaoTalk_20260501_115951853.jpg\"/><p>另一名宏泰閣男居民，見他落樓時推着大包海味，包括花膠、陳皮等，他坦言喜出望外，可以拾回珍藏的花膠等海味。</p><p>最Hit</p>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-01T05:54:53.866597+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":239,"images":8,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}